@page "/about"

@* ==================================================
    ABOUT PAGE
    Provides information about the WorkSync application
    and its educational purpose.
================================================== *@
<h1>About WorkSync</h1>

<p>
    WorkSync is a classroom-friendly Blazor leadership management
    application designed to help demonstrate:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>CRUD operations</li>
    <li>Role-based access concepts</li>
    <li>Dashboard reporting</li>
    <li>Entity Framework Core</li>
    <li>Blazor Server development</li>
</ul>

<p>
    No confidential or real Church information is stored in this application.
</p>